---
title: Picante Corn and Black Bean Stew with Guacamole and Spiced Tortilla Chips
description: This hearty, Mexican-inspired stew is packed with filling fibre and veggie goodness! Mashed beans and a splash of flavourful bean liquid are the secret to this stew's rich, creamy consistency. A dollop of guac and a squeeze of lime on top finishes it off with a burst of fresh, zingy flavour!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-epice-au-mais-et-aux-haricots-noirs-0f1a60a6.jpg
